  "rationale": "Repair note: removed block contracts that triggered the 'body' KeyError (header/content-block/form/footer) and rebuilt those sections from primitives + card/feature-item blocks whose copy dicts carry no required 'body' key. Order follows the one-scroll narrative: an inverse hero bookend (the sole accent + sanctioned display-over-media with a media-over-media overlap), then primary/panel editorial runs. Structural contrast is maximized: stack (hero), split (about, curator, newsletter), stack-fullbleed (gallery), interlock (mission, novel float-wrap+ghost), collage (heritage, novel with 1941/2023 ghost years + staggered timeline), cards on panel (visit info with the ticketing CTA and map), and stack (footer). Off-grid expansion is used deliberately in the two novel primary sections; every other section stays on grid, single-accent, radius-0, no cards on cream."
